{"tid":909030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國航母列根號將於明天訪問香港","createTime":"2018-11-20T04:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:12:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5b8c46655eb72497e9fa0808414c95897858d1","tid":909030,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"中美軍事及貿易關係緊張之際，美軍日前在菲律賓海進行「雙航母」演習，被指是針對中國。香港海事處的資料顯示，其中一艘參演的航母列根號，將聯同另外3艘美軍軍艦於周三（21日）訪問香港。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港海事處網站的抵港及離港船隻資料，列根號已經獲得批准，將於周三早上9時抵達香港，同行的軍艦還有神盾驅逐艦本福德號及卡迪斯沃巴號，以及神盾巡洋艦切斯勞維爾號。暫未知它們何時離港，而美軍尚未公布列根號等軍艦的最新動向。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181120/mobile/bkn-20181120110101395-1120_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181120%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181120110101395-1120_00822_001.html&d=pYblX2s1qceYPLHhGbA02tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=37d52295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181120/mobile/bkn-20181120110101395-1120_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"35ca2119ce034d058419aca638b569b35f46d65d","tid":909030,"uid":130693,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgHdGnQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgHdGnQ.gif&h=aa0319c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bba00150868327e18f96b54aa207cc283f2b8afe","tid":909030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"Come come come"},{"pid":"6b3b122707eaf63bf0f21e69eb083e3e2629bb85","tid":909030,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35ca2119ce034d058419aca638b569b35f46d65d","tid":909030,"uid":130693,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgHdGnQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgHdGnQ.gif&h=aa0319c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re